We have an issue. Checking again, there’s another 10 minute interval when the variable goes from 20 -&gt; 21.

fix.time &lt;- function (time) {
  suppressPackageStartupMessages(library(lubridate))

  # don't mess up NA values
  is_zero &lt;- time == 0

  scnds_since_midnight &lt;- 120 + (time-1)*300 + ifelse(time &gt; 6, 300, 0) + 
                          ifelse(time &gt; 9, 300, 0) + ifelse(time &gt; 20, 300, 0)

